Translated JSP include :

            if (_jspx_inited == false) {
                synchronized (this) {
                    if (_jspx_inited == false) {
                        _jspx_init();
                        _jspx_inited = true;
                    }
                }
            }
This is a double check locking idiom, but this doesn't work ! (see 
http://www.javaworld.com/javaworld/jw-02-2001/jw-0209-double_p.html)
